admin and content creater will add blogs
the user can only view the contents cannot add contents
both the roles will - register and login
                    - get authenticated

Registration process
    - user will enter the registration details and token will be generated
    - user will login with email and password this time a new token will be sent
    - this token will be used to identify the user for alll request and response
Protected Routes - Specific routes will be prottected    


